id=traffic-stats
name=Traffic Stats (vnstat-lite)
version=v1.0.1
versionCode=2
author=kaandikec
description=Pure-shell per-interface daily RX/TX accumulator (vnstat-lite). Polls /proc/net/dev every 60s; daily DB at /data/traffic-stats/. Survives kernel counter resets. Read via statusbot /traffic_history. Requires bin-utils v1.3.0+.
updateJson=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dikeckaan/magisk-zte-f50-traffic-stats/main/update.json
